_Pool_2.jpg</Url><Width>360</Width><Height>252</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/IBZ-92hotel_Swimming_Pool_2_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>80</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>60</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>SwimmingPool</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>The hotel?s recent refurbishment has been recognised with its upgrade to 4-star status, and it is now one of the few hotels in the area to have reached these high standards. Although your every need will be catered for by our facilities and courteous, helpful staff you may wish to explore the town and for this there is a half hourly bus service to the town centre from the hotel.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>Situated 4km from Ibiza town with beautiful views of the Dalt Vila , Playa Den Bossa is a resort which is popular with all types of holidaymakers from families to younger adults wanting to enjoy the nightlife . Of course being the home of Space, the most well known nightclub in Europe, needless to say the needs of the younger tourist are well catered for but there is a whole lot more to this resort than that.    The long golden sands provide plenty of scope for relaxation, play and watersports with the sea providing safe shallow waters for the children. There are plenty of family friendly cafes and bars directly on the sea front and lots for the kids to do while mum and dad relax. If you fancy a change from sea bathing then the resort also offers a large water park. Other entertainment on offer in Playa Den Bossa includes a bowling centre with trampolines and mini-golf and lots of playgrounds and amusement centre?s for the kids which are floodlight for night time outings. There is also the opportunity for the more energetic to follow a walking or cycling route( approx 19km) which passes from the resort beach through the beach at Es Codolar and then on to the nature reserve at Ses Salines home of the stunning salt flats of Ibiza.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>Modern Ibiza style</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>2 Bar Cafe Restaurant on the beach</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>Modern and spacious Lobby area</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Whirlpool</Code><Text>Whirlpool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HandicapAccessible</Code><Text>Handicap accessible</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MoneyExchange</Code><Text>Money exchange</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CheckIn24hr</Code><Text>24hr. CheckIn</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Reception24hr</Code><Text>24hr. Reception</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Supermarket</Code><Text>Supermarket</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>DiscoClub</Code><Text>Disco / Club</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ConferenceRoom</Code><Text>Conference Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>GameRoom</Code><Text>GameRoom</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVRoom</Code><Text>TV Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MedicalService</Code><Text>Medical Service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>FreshWaterPool</Code><Text>Fresh Water Pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ChildrenPool</Code><Text>Children's pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>SunLounge</Code><Text>SunLounge</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Parasol</Code><Text>Parasol</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>SunBathingTerrace</Code><Text>Sun Bath